      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor door dings, and the interior upholstery shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and new tires in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
