    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute gem! I'm parting ways with my car and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels brand new. It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014super clean inside and out, runs like a dream, and hasn't a single scratch on it. If you're looking for something that looks and drives perfectly, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering: the S65 4.0L V8. This specimen boasts a linear power band culminating in an 8,400 RPM redline, with preventative rod bearing replacement already performed using VAC coated bearings and ARP bolts. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) provides instantaneous gear synchronization, paired with the Competition Package (ZCP) which optimizes the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and dynamic stability mapping for increased lateral grip. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. All body panels show original VIN tags and consistent paint thickness, reflecting a climate-controlled life. The interior is finished in pristine Novillo leather, with the side bolsters and Alcantara surfaces showing no signs of friction wear or UV-induced degradation.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless paint. Interior like new. Mechanically perfect. Garage kept. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior is finished in a flawless coat, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, and has been protected since day one with a multi-layer ceramic coating. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather upholstery remains supple without any bolster wear, creasing, or fading. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment, retaining its original factory scent. Every technological feature, including the navigation system, heated seating, and driver-assist suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, having undergone every scheduled service at the local flagship dealership\u2014full documentation and a clean history report are available for review. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed, representing a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a showroom-quality specimen.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
