    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle has been preserved to an exacting standard, maintaining its original showroom-fresh aesthetic and peak mechanical integrity. Offering uncompromising quality and a meticulously documented provenance, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly pristine asset.",
      "price": 47500.0,
